                     <interp inst="t18020113-5-off19" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020113-5-off19" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020113-5-cd20" type="crimeDate">27th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020113-5-off19 t18020113-5-cd20"></join>, a counterpane, value 5s. a a set of fire irons, value 8s. a sin candle box, value 6d. and a pound of candles, value 10d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18020113-5-victim82" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Smart
                        <interp inst="t18020113-5-victim82" type="surname" value="Smart"></interp>
